        "min_age": 21,
        "max_age": 41,
        "vacancy": 10,
        "experience": "4-5",
        "edu_title_id": 8,
        "job_desc": "<p>We are looking for a competent <strong>Camp Boss</strong> to oversee daily onboard operations, including catering services, accommodation management, hygiene compliance, inventory control, and team supervision. The role requires solid offshore experience, food safety certification, computer proficiency, and a strong background in cooking or baking.</p>",
        "job_requirement": "<p><br></p><table><tbody><tr><td data-row=\"1\">Overall Administration of assigned locations to ensure the highest quality of services to our clients.</td></tr></tbody></table><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Reports to the Operations Manager on all contractual concerns and achievements.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ensures smooth running of operations according to the guidelines of the Contract and ensures that all contractual Obligations are met.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Control &amp; Maintain company service quality and client satisfaction at the best level.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Provides guidelines to Mid - management, Maintains total control on rules and regulations and monitors administration procedures. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ensures reports and logs are always maintained for easy reference and access. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Demonstrate interpersonal and communication skills to effectively communicate and interact with Customers and Co-workers in a courteous and professional manner.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Maintains positive and effective working relationships with staff.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ensures that a team-oriented environment is built and sustained<strong>.</strong></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Maintains quality and timeliness at work.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Analytical skills to effectively identify and resolve purchasing, payroll, accounting, and other problems in line with supervisors.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Pro-active to follow up on projects and complete assignments in a timely manner.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ability to effectively communicate department mission, organization, activities, and program information resources to internal and external customers.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Discretion and ability to maintain confidentiality of information and issues as appropriate, including payroll and personnel information.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Closely monitors term and conditions of contracts with clients and ensures that the concerned staff on site is aware of Contractual Obligations.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ensure proper people development and their security onboard. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Proper documentation and training matrix update daily basis. And Maintain the X-Function relationship.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Arranging Food Provision &amp; delivery.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Responsible for Store managements without storekeeper</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Month end document (will be described by line supervisor) submission as per company timeline.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Daily report and summary submission online and physical, soft copy with office on time.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Handle Monthly onboard client audit.</li></ol>",
        "recruitment_process": "<p><strong><u>Abilities:</u></strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Able to manage onboard over all operation in absence of Campboss, Handle to campboss job on emergencies situation.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ability to give and follow oral or written instruction and establish procedures.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ability to read, write, speak English,</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>To run computers very well- Excel, World, outlook (Ms. Office).</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ability to analyze guest satisfaction, and able to use information to create strategies to improve satisfaction.</li></ol><p><br></p><p><strong><u>Physical Report Required:</u></strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Physical efforts (lifting and carrying).</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Frequent prolonged standing and walking.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Considerable reaching, stopping, bending, kneeling, and crouching.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Exposed to hot and humid work environment. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Exposed to heat, wetness, and odor in the kitchen and/or patient areas.</li></ol><p><br></p><p><strong><u>Additional Requirement:</u></strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit; background-color: transparent;\">Seaman Book Required</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Valid Passport (minimum 1-year validity).</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Candidates previously block-listed in Saudi Arabia are not eligible.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Candidates with previous GAMCA medical unfit status are not allowed. </span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Good communication and interpersonal skills</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit; background-color: transparent;\">Gulf returnees will be preferred.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit; background-color: transparent;\">Must be experienced.</span></li></ol>",
