        "employment_type": "full_time",
        "gender": "male",
        "min_age": 21,
        "max_age": 35,
        "vacancy": 10,
        "experience": "2-3",
        "edu_title_id": 4,
        "job_desc": "<p>We are looking for a disciplined Storekeeper to ensure proper receiving, storage, issuance, and security of food supplies, maintaining full compliance with safety standards, documentation requirements, and Ligabue operational policies. The role requires strong attention to hygiene, temperature monitoring, inventory control, and workplace safety across all food service operations.</p>",
        "job_requirement": "<ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Support full hospitality and kitchen operations in daily meal production and service.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Assist in meat cutting, trimming, deboning, portioning, and proper storage.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Prepare raw materials for cooking, including marination, washing, and pre-prep activities.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Maintain strict food safety, hygiene, and sanitation standards in all work areas.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ensure proper labeling, FIFO rotation, and expiry date control of food items.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Operate kitchen tools and equipment safely and responsibly.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Assist in stock receiving, checking quality, and organizing cold storage and dry storage.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Keep workstations clean, organized, and compliant with safety regulations.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Follow supervisor instructions and support smooth service during peak hours.</li></ol>",
        "recruitment_process": "<ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Seaman Book Required</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Valid Passport (minimum 1-year validity).</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Candidates previously block-listed in Saudi Arabia are not eligible.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Candidates with previous GAMCA medical unfit status are not allowed. </span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Good communication and interpersonal skills</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit; background-color: transparent;\">Gulf returnees will be preferred.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Food Safety Knowledge</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit; background-color: transparent;\">Must be experienced.</span></li></ol>",
