        "job_title": "Bakery and Pastry Chef",
        "slug": "ligabue-bakeryman-and-pastry-chef",
        "priority": 4,
        "address": null,
        "company_name": "Ligabue",
        "industry_name": "Catering",
        "is_active": 1,
        "salary_type": "monthly",
        "currency": "SAR",
        "min_salary": 2500,
        "max_salary": 2800,
        "employment_type": "full_time",
        "gender": "male",
        "min_age": 21,
        "max_age": 38,
        "vacancy": 25,
        "experience": "5-6",
        "edu_title_id": 3,
        "job_desc": "<p>The <strong>BAKERYMAN &amp; PASTRY CHEF</strong> is responsible for managing day-to-day food production, maintaining quality, and ensuring that all meals are prepared according to recipes and standards set by the Camp Boss and Executive Chef. The role requires leadership, strong culinary skills, and the ability to supervise the entire kitchen team during operations.</p>",
        "job_requirement": "<p><strong>1.Job Scope Listed but not Limited to:</strong></p><p>Responsible for Production of Food following instruction from Camp boss &amp; Executive Chef, all preparation must be done as per recipe given.  </p><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>As per immediate Chef Cook/Campboss instructions, assist them in the direction of all aspects of food production by leading all kitchen employees, including cooks, junior cooks, Asst. cooks, Dish washers and Waiters as assigned.</li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Assure that all preparations are accurately and efficiently cooked. Make sure that subordinates are following recipes and portion control for all food products prior to cooking. Also perform other duties in the areas of food and final preparation including plating and garnishing of cooked items and preparing appropriate garnishes for all hot and cold food item. </li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Supervise all cooks in all levels plus overlooking the proper functioning of the dish washing department.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ensures Personal Hygiene standards, uniform code of behaviors among all staff.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Support food provision- Loading &amp; Unloading.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Establish, Review &amp; follow company standard menu planning as per contractual agreement with client and Camp Boss.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Implies Health and Safety measures including code of Accident prevention.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Responsible for cleaning and deep cleaning of all related individual designated areas production.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ensure Recipe Card follow up while preparing of meal as per SOP procedures.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Follow up the day to-day instruction given by camp boss &amp; executive chef and ensures the correct serving portions followed.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ensure that working area is kept clean and organized all the time and applies the rules – “Clean as You Go.”</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Checks all food preparation and serving, be present during food service time from opening to closing for smooth operation.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Co-ordinates with co-workers to make smooth operation- giving helping hand when its needed.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Constant attention must be paid to Safe Work Practices, immediately addressing any unsafe act witnessed. This applies to all Food &amp; service staffs.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>If required assist the Camp Boss during receiving commissary on board.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Review and prepare weekly Purchase Order with the camp boss as per daily menu requirement and Cost target.</li></ol><p><br></p><p><strong>2. <u>Abilities:</u></strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Able to manage onboard over all operation in absence of Camp boss, Handle to camp boss job on emergencies situation.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ability to give and follow oral or written instruction and establish procedures.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ability to read a limited of two and tree syllable words and to recognize similarities different between numbers.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Ability to analyze guest satisfaction, and able to use information to create strategies to improve satisfaction.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><br></li></ol><p><strong>3.<u>Physical Report Required:</u></strong></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Physical efforts (lifting and carrying).</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Frequent prolonged standing and walking.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Considerable reaching, stopping, bending, kneeling, and crouching.</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Exposed to hot and humid work environment. </li></ol>",
        "recruitment_process": "<ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span>Seaman Book Required</li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Valid Passport (minimum 1-year validity).</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Candidates previously block-listed in Saudi Arabia are not eligible.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Candidates with previous GAMCA medical unfit status are not allowed. </span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">Good communication and interpersonal skills</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit; background-color: transparent;\">Gulf returnees will be preferred.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"color: inherit; background-color: transparent;\">Must be experienced.</span></li></ol>",
